At the 2020 census, Mountainair had 884 people, 447 households, and 323 families residing within the town. The racial makeup of the town was 58.48% [[White Americans|White]], 2.15% [[Native Americans in the United States|Native Americans]], 2.03% [[African Americans|African American]], 0.04% [[Asian Americans|Asian]], 0.02% [[Pacific Islander Americans|Pacific Islander]], 18.55% from other races, and 18.10% from two or more races. [[Hispanic and Latino Americans|Hispanic or Latino]] of any race were 50.11% of the population.

